message: I understand that a 10-year non-compete period may seem extensive. However, it ensures market stability and allows us to fully integrate Rio Copa Foods into our operations. This period also provides ample time for us to honor and continue the legacy of the Costa family in Santa Cruz. Let's consider this as a long-term investment for both parties.
